(16, 85, 'About Venison Meat SA', 'about-venison-meat-sa', '<img src="images/safrican.jpg"><p>Venison Meat SA was formed by Willie Joubert, who together with his father formed Safrican Leisure Properties over 30 years ago. As a result they have been involved in every aspect of conservation - from game farming, game breed- ing and game capture to eco- development and management of some of the best wildlife and tourism destinations in Southern Africa.</p>\r\n<p class="about-venison">Venison Meat SA is a market leader with the first registered mobile game abattoir in Southern Africa. This mobile abattoir gives us a tangible advantage, as we can ensure that the harvesting and processing is conducted in accordance with the highest standards, from start to finish.</p>\r\n<p class="about-venison">Our registered mobile abattoir gives us the ability to move throughout the country, only sourcing venison from game farmers who share our same passion and commitment to sustainable game conservation. Venison Meat SA has procured the services of industry experts in various fields, who take pride in delivering only the best “From Nature’s Kitchen to Yours”!</p>\r\n<p class="about-venison">We have also partnered with registered, accredited facilities and institutions with whom we are building a sustainable, long- term working relationship, to ensure that our customers consistently receive only the very best products.</p>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<ul class="gallery-link">\r\n<li>\r\n<a title="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet" href="images/gallery-1.jpg" rel="example_group">\r\n<img src="images/gallery-1.jpg" alt="">\r\n</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a title="" href="images/gallery-2.jpg" rel="example_group">\r\n<img src="images/gallery-2.jpg" alt="">\r\n</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a title="" href="images/gallery-3.jpg" rel="example_group">\r\n<img src="images/gallery-3.jpg" alt="">\r\n</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a title="" href="images/gallery-4.jpg" rel="example_group">\r\n<img class="last" src="ima