(99, 84, 'WINNING RECIPES', '', '<div class="row tips_thumb">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12 text-left">\r\n<h4>WINNING RECIPES</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-4">\r\n<div class="mask_holder">\r\n<a href="chilli-and-ginger-venison-in-leattuce-leaves"><img src="images/news_img/tips-1.png"></a>\r\n<div class="mask"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="chilli-and-ginger-venison-in-leattuce-leaves">Chilli and ginger venison in leattuce leaves</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-4">\r\n<div class="mask_holder">\r\n<a href="chilli-and-ginger-venison-in-leattuce-leaves"><img src="images/news_img/tips-2.png"></a>\r\n<div class="mask"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="chilli-and-ginger-venison-in-leattuce-leaves">Succulent braised venison</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-4">\r\n<div class="mask_holder">\r\n<a href="chilli-and-ginger-venison-in-leattuce-leaves"><img src="images/news_img/tips-3.png"></a>\r\n<div class="mask"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="chilli-and-ginger-venison-in-leattuce-leaves">Pan fried venison with blackberry sauce</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 'position-15', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{"prepare_content":"0","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"WINNING RECIPES","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static","module_tag":"div","bootstrap_size":"0","header_tag":"h3","header_class":"","style":"0"}', 0, '*'),
(100, 86, 'Contributing to sustainable conservation', '', '<img src="images/main-about.jpg">\r\n<p> The astonishing increase in game numbers over a very short period has occurred as a result of holistic approach to conservation that includes a balance between eco-tourism, investment, recreational hunting, game farming and wildlife translocations. As a result, there is more land under wildlife production and more wildlife itself in this country now than at any other time over the last 100 years. </p>\r\n<h2>\r\n“large game animals\r\n<strong> have increased nearly </strong>\r\n40 times since 1964”\r\n</h2>\r\n<p> The industries that have grown up around wildlife contribute some R8 Billion annually to the economy. These wildlife based industries also provide 3 ½ times more and better skilled jobs, at salaries and wages more than 5 1/2 times higher than did the domestic livestock industry that, for the most part, they replaced. The equivalent amount of land converted from livestock to game, has thus transformed the land based agricultural economy in South African, whilst massively expanding the net-worth of both the product harvested and the land itself </p>', 1, 'position-7', 680, '2014-11-20 13:08:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"0","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":" about_img_theme","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static","module_tag":"div","bootstrap_size":"0","header_tag":"h3","header_class":"","style":"0"}', 0, '*'),
